      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "一个受迫摆动的振子，轨迹在相空间里绕来绕去，缠成一团乱麻。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "看久了只觉得混乱，很难判断它到底是规律还是混沌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "庞加莱想了一个巧妙的办法，把这团乱麻压成一张清爽的点图。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "strobe",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "strobe-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/strobe-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "驱动力有固定周期，就像一盏按节拍闪烁的频闪灯。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "strobe",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "strobe-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/strobe-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "每过一个驱动周期，我们只记录此刻的位置和速度，其余时间都不看。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "strobe",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "strobe-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/strobe-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "连续的轨迹于是被抽稀成一串离散的采样点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "point",
      "line_id": "pt-1",
      "filename": "point-pt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/point-pt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "这些点落在相空间的一张截面上，就是庞加莱截面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "point",
      "line_id": "pt-2",
      "filename": "point-pt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/poincare-section/xiaoxiao/point-pt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "高维的连续运动，被降成了二维平面上一堆好读的点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "poincare-section",
      "section_id": "point",
      "line_id": "pt-3",
